# Iterazioni

``` cpp
int val, total = 0, count = 0;
cout << "Val (-1 to finish)? ";
cin >> val;
while (val != -1) {
    total += val;
    ++count;
    cout << "Val (-1 to finish)? ";
    cin >> val;
}
if (count > 0) {
    cout << "Avg: " << total / float(count) << "\n";
}
```

>

[Iterazioni in Python](p1-algoritmi.html#24)
<br>
